com.davidsoergel.trees

Interface NodeNamer<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntegerGeneratingNodeNamer, IntegerNodeNamer, RequireExistingNodeNamer, StringIntegerNodeNamer, StringNodeNamer

    public interface NodeNamer<T>
    A factory for names to be applied to phylogeny nodes. Generally used to add incrementing IDs to internal nodes of a tree for which only the leaves have known names.
    Version:
    $Id: NodeNamer.java 262 2009-03-31 20:04:18Z soergel $
    Author:
    David Soergel
